subject: Horse Racing
Rachel Alexandra (Race Horse)
Preakness Stakes
lead_paragraph: Rachel Alexandra, the 2009 Preakness and horse of the year winner who is now a broodmare, is recuperating from a near-fatal infection she developed after foaling in February.
